latestIgtvVideos.title: thankyou 2020!
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Made this video 4 months ago and I’ve watched it over so many times but I’m posting it today because I was thinking if I could summarise what my fav moments are from 2020 & I guess this video says it all. Reflecting on a year that has had so many highs and so many lows. A year that has taught us to value time and our loved ones. As turbulent as this year was, I personally consider myself very fortunate because I had a home that I could spend quality time with my family in. I would never make it to the other side without these faces🤍 ngl, we’ve had our share of days full of trepidation BUT we’ve also had a fucking blast! We didn’t really need much other than each other’s company (and cheetos maybe). So even though you were mostly a crappy year, I’m so grateful🤞🏻THANKYOU 2020!

latestPosts.caption:
performer by day, heartbroken at night! 
.
.
I recorded this “save your tears” cover with @johmusicx & it’s been sat on my phone for ages… 
I had this extravagant idea which I never got around executing & then 2 days back I just decided to go for it?! I’m so happy with how this turned out…

the holidays can be a very overwhelming/ lonely time & seeing everyone’s celebrations displayed on social media often makes us feel shitty about our own selves, makes us question all the decisions we’ve made that led us HERE (to the present). 

Take this time to just do the little things that will make you happy because in the grand scheme of things, I promise, it always works out ✨ 

MERRY CHRISTMAS🫶🏻
